Gould Inc said itregistered to offer two mln shares of convertible exchangeablepreferred stock.    Gould said the proposed new issue will be underwritten byFirst Boston Corp and Kidder, Peabody and Co Inc.    In a registration statement filed with the Securities andExchange Commission, Gould said the shares will be convertibleat any time into Gould common.    The shares also will be exchangeable into Gould convertiblesubordinated debentures at a rate of 50 dlrs principal amountper debenture. Reuter&#3;